data.title: Organizations – Heritage League of Kansas City
data.text:
Member Organizations of The Heritage League of Greater Kansas City

So you’re interested in history? Heritage League of Greater Kansas City members are, too.

Members of The Heritage League of Greater Kansas City include individuals as well as public and private entities, each having a similar interest and objective – the preservation and celebration of American history as it relates to local, regional and Missouri/Kansas State History.

We encourage you to visit or contact our institutional members for more information about their services and programs. These organizations may also invite membership offering additional benefits. The list below details most of our institutional members. Please contact any member of the Board of Directors for comments or corrections. If you would like to become a member, please visit the membership page.
